{"tid":60471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"離婚","createTime":"2016-12-30T12:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T13:10:01.000Z","uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdcdc1394ef149a2d6d4b477ef0c305ba400e53d","tid":60471,"uid":48897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"父母終於離婚啦<br />\n今日做仔嘅我拎住媽封離婚申請書比阿爸簽<br />\n好耐無同過阿爸食飯<br />\n食到尾我先敢拎封信出黎同佢講<br />\n見到佢都眼濕濕<br />\n雖然分開咗咁多年<br />\n但係始終會有傷心<br />\n我都以為自己唔介意<br />\n但係原來都好心up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/205715_de73d9ede4551b36d67d8ef33c0afc99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F205715_de73d9ede4551b36d67d8ef33c0afc99.jpg&h=64614d87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n希望佢哋兩個都可以放低"},{"pid":"e078c416c30b5707bd9273248d304e21e15146a2","tid":60471,"uid":48897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"其實有時好羨幕人地一家人可以齊齊整整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13c8075b5a73f46d0851f43420bffb3e7582fed","tid":60471,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T13:10:01.000Z","msg":"原因係乜"}]}